OL,4,Cline of traffic jailed
OL,6,FA driver who caused three other
OL,7,Fmotorists devastating injuries in a
OL,8,Fcrash as he tried to overtake a
OL,9,Fmotorbike on a country road has been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FPeter Buttery, 64, from Goole, was in
OL,13,Fa line of traffic on the B1248, near
OL,14,FMalton, North Yorkshire, when he tried
OL,15,Fto pass a Ural motorcycle near a bend.
OL,17,FAs he did so, a Mazda MX5, travelling
OL,18,Fin the opposite direction, collided
OL,19,Fwith Buttery's Fiat and the
OL,20,Fmotorcycle, causing huge damage.
