OL,6,FThe biker, a man in his 60s, suffered
OL,7,Flife-threatening injuries including
OL,8,Fbroken vertebrae, broken ribs, a
OL,9,Fbroken wrist, a punctured lung and
OL,10,Fother internal injuries.
OL,12,FTwo people in the Mazda MX5 suffered
OL,13,Fserious injuries, including broken
OL,14,Fbones, facial scarring and nerve
OL,15,Fdamage.
OL,17,FFollowing the incident, which happened
OL,18,Fon the afternoon of 6 August 2021,
OL,19,FButtery was charged with three counts
OL,20,Fof causing serious injury by dangerous
OL,21,Fdriving.
