OL,4,Cline of traffic jailed
OL,6,FHe was found guilty following a trial
OL,7,Fat Hull Crown Court and was jailed for
OL,8,Fthree years and 10 months.
OL,10,FIn a statement given to the court, the
OL,11,Finjured motorcyclist said: "The
OL,12,Fcollision forever will have a profound
OL,13,Feffect on me, physically and mentally."
OL,15,FHe described not being able to walk
OL,16,Fmore than 200 yards without the use of
OL,17,Fa walking stick, bend over, have a
OL,18,Fbath, or get an uninterrupted night's
OL,19,Fsleep.
