OL,6,FHe added: "One thing that I still
OL,7,Fstruggle with is that I can never
OL,8,Fcanoe, sail, go camping, backpacking
OL,9,For hiking ever again. It really hurts
OL,10,Fto know this. I am trying my hardest
OL,11,Fto have some sort of normal life, but
OL,12,Fit's hard."
OL,14,FTraffic officer Joseph Schramm, of
OL,15,FNorth Yorkshire Police, said: "The
OL,16,Fevidence showed that Buttery was on
OL,17,Fthe wrong side of the road leading up
OL,18,Fto the collision, conducting an
OL,19,Fovertake in a dangerous location.
